        <mxCell id="Wy9DJU4JKrCk-EyFJ-PD-39" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontSize=19;fontColor=default;labelBackgroundColor=default;fontStyle=0;" value="&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 22pt; text-indent: -22pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Wingdings; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;l&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;Access Control&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;: Referer-based hotlink protection, URL authentication, IP/User-Agent (UA) allowlist/denylist, and remote authentication&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 22pt; text-indent: -22pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Wingdings; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;l&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;Attack Protection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;: Integration with DDoS Protection for large-scale attack mitigation, CC attack protection via request rate limiting, and potential sandbox isolation upon detection of abnormal traffic surges&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 22pt; text-indent: -22pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Wingdings; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;l&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;Transport Security&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;: HTTPS encryption, TLS version control, HSTS, OCSP Stapling, and mutual TLS (client certificate authentication)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 22pt; text-indent: -22pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Wingdings; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;l&lt;span style=&quot;font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-width: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;Origin Protection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style=&quot;font-family: system-ui, serif; color: rgb(24, 24, 24);&quot;&gt;: Origin server IP is hidden; users must add Alibaba Cloud CDN’s back-to-origin IP ranges to their origin firewall or WAF allowlist to prevent blocking&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 22pt; text-indent: -22pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;&quot;&gt;Bot Management&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 3pt; margin-left: 22pt; text-indent: -22pt; line-height: 18pt; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-teams=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Static Origin / Object Storage / Web Origin&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="303.48" width="830" x="380" y="170" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="oQbcHvXXmp1J8hQ4mMWe-7" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;labelBackgroundColor=default;" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;; line-height: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Secure service-to-service communication&lt;/strong&gt; using &lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;mutual TLS (mTLS)&lt;/strong&gt;, along with &lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;identity-based authentication and authorization&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automatic load balancing&lt;/strong&gt; for &lt;strong&gt;HTTP/HTTPS, gRPC, WebSocket, and TCP&lt;/strong&gt; traffic.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fine-grained traffic control&lt;/strong&gt; using rich routing rules, including &lt;strong&gt;retries, failover, and fault injection&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;Support for &lt;strong&gt;robust access control, rate limiting&lt;/strong&gt;, and other &lt;strong&gt;extensible policy mechanisms&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 19px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Full observability&lt;/strong&gt; of all traffic within the cluster—including &lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;ingress and egress traffic&lt;/strong&gt;—with &lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;default metrics, log collection, and distributed tracing&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="320" width="720" x="2130" y="1719" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
